[thinking] **Considering initialization and coverage**
[thinking] 
[thinking] It seems that Native Image might initialize at build time, while application classes operate at runtime, depending on the JDK. If the initialization occurs during the image build, the call sites wouldn't be available at runtime. I'm thinking that coverage could come from Java agents running on the JVM. We might just need to focus on tests for this. So, I'll need to create a file for this purpose.
